.Dd October 15, 2007
.Dt MAINBUS 4 evbppc
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm mainbus
.Nd Processor bus support
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "cpc0 at mainbus0"
.Cd "cs0  at mainbus0 addr 0x7fe00000"
.Cd "rtc0 at mainbus0 addr 0x7ff00000"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
provides support for the processor bus on the Artesyn PM/PPC.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr cpc 4 ,
.Xr cs 4 ,
.Xr rtc 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver
appeared in
.Nx 2.0 .
